      "review_summary": "The PR changes `resolveConfigEnvVars` so whole-value `${VAR}` references whose resolved text parses as a JSON array or object return arrays or objects, with focused tests for coercion and passthrough cases.\n\nPR surface: Source +38, Tests +58. Total +96 across 2 files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. for the review findings by source inspection: config loading runs substitution before validation, and the current write-back preservation only restores string incoming values against string parsed refs. I did not run tests because this review is read-only.",
